{"tid":1144747,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湊女最重要？港媽背囊砸人腳　受害者出聲反被鬧？","createTime":"2019-05-08T09:04:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T13:18:49.000Z","uid":225464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fdb610f34239f525816ba578985de8f8355e2a49","tid":1144747,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"湊女最重要？港媽背囊砸人腳 受害者出聲反被鬧？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JkI7ua\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JkI7ua&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2Fcqy4iG8TIfC1p449sO1N5Ck%3D&h=3e0f4237\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JkI7ua</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190508/photo/bkn-20190508163007316-0508_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190508170026\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190508%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190508163007316-0508_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190508170026&h=43c0d64c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解唔抱住個背囊？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有女乘客於周三（8日）在Facebook群組「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」發貼指，當日該港媽與女兒坐在巴士下層，惟港媽將背囊放地下時，卻一直壓着坐在對面座的她雙腳。<br />\n<br />\n她曾向該港媽反映並要求港媽移開背囊，惟港媽理直氣壯地指︰「會頂住個女隻腳」。她頓時大怒︰「但你依家砸住我對腳呀阿姐。你自己就擘大對髀嚟坐」。<br />\n<br />\n女乘客事後在貼文抱怨指：「至弊我已遇到佢2次，擔心日日都遇到佢，我諗冇人會鍾意自己對腳畀人砸住」。"},{"pid":"6348b2f420e9b2ff1bf43f32bb7bbbbe52bec4f2","tid":1144747,"uid":220701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:07:26.000Z","msg":"扔出街咪得"},{"pid":"53b09912e11e48cec251a90f9c46089578696c34","tid":1144747,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:08:20.000Z","msg":"下次攞隻腳頂返佢個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ab11b8e639735f9794cd131e5432490a2428a8","tid":1144747,"uid":167426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:37:20.000Z","msg":"嗰老母自撚私到<br />\n真係盡顯香港精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0937793b61fe3a9bee8fda78d1f5b9c7eb088d","tid":1144747,"uid":123842